  "title": "Beauty Consultant",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Provide professional skin care advice to customers.</li>\n  <li>Recommend skin care products to customers.</li>\n  <li>Build and establish good rapport with customers.</li>\n  <li>Maintain general housekeeping duties and maintenance of the cleanliness of the outlet.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Cidesco, ITE, CIBTAC and other beauty related qualifications.</li>\n  <li>Positive and willing to learn attitude.</li>\n  <li>Good communication and Interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Service Oriented and customer focused.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\n  <li>Preferably Junior Executive specialized in Personal Care/Beauty/Fitness Service or equivalent.</li>\n</ul>",
